<h2 id="using-contents">Using contents</h2>

<p>Contents is an in-page navigation to guide the user through a series of pages that are linked together.</p>

<p>It should be used on information pages and should be positioned at the top, just below the page title.</p>

<p>It shouldn’t be used to link to other sections of the website or pages that aren’t grouped together.</p>
